item.title: Taurus in roses
item.description:
This work was delivered on the second day of participation in the Saint-Petersburg Tattoo Weekend 2017.

The final work is based on the original design by Yana Gogo, which she made in Shanghai in early 2017. It has quite a history. For the Saint-Petersburg event’s model, according to her wishes, Yana changed the flowers into roses. We’re sure she has a lot to tell us about the excellent works she made and her experience of participation.

Cannot wait to hear more about this work from the artist and the new owner.
